the flag itself is divided horizontally in two the top band is yellow and the bottom band is red the yellow colour denotes the gold from the earth as well as the virtues of justice clemency benevolence the socalled mundane qualities defined as nobility excellence richness generosity splendour health steadfastness joy and prosperity long life eternity power and constancy  the red colour denotes the virtue of charity as well as the qualities of bravery nobility values audacity victory honour and furor colombians call it the blood of their people
